  "3183760": {
    "name": "SpeedRunners 2: King of Speed",
    "steam_appid": 3183760,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/2a8dac4641b472ffefb708f0e67361a0.poster.avif?t=1772093336\" width=616 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/2a8dac4641b472ffefb708f0e67361a0.webm?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/2a8dac4641b472ffefb708f0e67361a0.mp4?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/39eda9dc339f27ce3ee2119b8ed0a81a.poster.avif?t=1772093336\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/39eda9dc339f27ce3ee2119b8ed0a81a.webm?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/39eda9dc339f27ce3ee2119b8ed0a81a.mp4?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《极速跑者》的原创多玩家游玩形式堪称永不过时之经典，被广大玩家冠以“2D平台游戏中的《马里奥赛车》”的美名。在续作中，我们的目标是将这一独特的“《极速跑者》感受”带入新纪元，既不破坏其运动系统的深度与流畅度，同时又要保证其易于上手。在此基础上，《速度之王》还引入了充满活力的高清晰度图形以及更加优化的网络参数。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/af51547ede4a4b453b3c6ad240fbf5f6.poster.avif?t=1772093336\" width=616 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/af51547ede4a4b453b3c6ad240fbf5f6.webm?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/af51547ede4a4b453b3c6ad240fbf5f6.mp4?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/a721c80fc3d6bbb9a395855693af5c32.poster.avif?t=1772093336\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/a721c80fc3d6bbb9a395855693af5c32.webm?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/a721c80fc3d6bbb9a395855693af5c32.mp4?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为2010年代最受欢迎的独立开发游戏之一的续作，《极速跑者2：速度之王》是一款快节奏的竞赛型平台游戏。充满活力的角色阵容由离经叛道的超级英雄组成，其中既有旧人回归，也有新人加入；从中挑选一个你喜欢的角色，在疯狂的竞速比赛中直面你的对手。每个游戏大厅可容纳多达8位玩家，本地或线上均可。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/648b769fb2f2bb82d70dfcf557c1eecc.poster.avif?t=1772093336\" width=616 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/648b769fb2f2bb82d70dfcf557c1eecc.webm?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/648b769fb2f2bb82d70dfcf557c1eecc.mp4?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/b24488dd38cc8876300fb650b0e6083a.poster.avif?t=1772093336\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/b24488dd38cc8876300fb650b0e6083a.webm?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/b24488dd38cc8876300fb650b0e6083a.mp4?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的目标是采取一切必要手段取得领先并保住头名位置，在此过程中你的对手将会一个接着一个被不断溃缩的火圈吞噬。准备好玩命奔跑，跨越多条以复古未来风世界为背景的美丽赛道，其灵感来源于1960年代的超级英雄乌托邦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/936bf48c77f47744505af2b4e2b5c00a.poster.avif?t=1772093336\" width=616 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/936bf48c77f47744505af2b4e2b5c00a.webm?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/936bf48c77f47744505af2b4e2b5c00a.mp4?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/38c651f744a76fa260fa69d51299032a.poster.avif?t=1772093336\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/38c651f744a76fa260fa69d51299032a.webm?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/38c651f744a76fa260fa69d51299032a.mp4?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将对手击出屏幕之外，通过使用各种强大的道具来扼杀竞争，其中包括：导弹、陷阱、冰冻射线，或是一个可用于将面前奔跑者拉开的金钩爪。玷污友谊、摧毁控制器并在奔跑途中做出千钧一发的决策，一切只为成为真正的速度之王！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/b5eb620c6a4c9549253e33840cfb8f7d.poster.avif?t=1772093336\" width=616 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/b5eb620c6a4c9549253e33840cfb8f7d.webm?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/b5eb620c6a4c9549253e33840cfb8f7d.mp4?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/103aaf4311098aa354fe5966d1d40962.poster.avif?t=1772093336\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/103aaf4311098aa354fe5966d1d40962.webm?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/103aaf4311098aa354fe5966d1d40962.mp4?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >熟悉经过巧妙设计的地图的布局，并掌握直观而深奥的运动机制。记住各种机关的位置，包括加速垫、道具、墙壁跳跃区域、障碍物、可以钩住的蓝色天花板，以及可供开关通道的控制杆。奔跑、跳跃、滑行加上摇荡，一路奔向胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/5dd50e4cecc5ae23aaedaefa8f597628.poster.avif?t=1772093336\" width=616 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/5dd50e4cecc5ae23aaedaefa8f597628.webm?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/5dd50e4cecc5ae23aaedaefa8f597628.mp4?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/fb1feb2520c30f6fa6a9ba77dc09c3ce.poster.avif?t=1772093336\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/fb1feb2520c30f6fa6a9ba77dc09c3ce.webm?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183760/extras/fb1feb2520c30f6fa6a9ba77dc09c3ce.mp4?t=1772093336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《极速跑者2》是一款可支持轻松享乐的竞赛游戏，但它也拥有很高的技能天花板，让玩家可以花费成百上千个小时来磨练自己的极速奔跑绝技。加入一个专注于奉献的社区以参与各种锦标赛、打造定制挑战并在排行榜上力争上游，或者创建私人游戏大厅和你的好友共享轻松的玩家对战乐趣。</p>",
